81
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:45,910
U-Uh...

82
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:48,500
My name is Angela.

83
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,670
N-Nice to meet you.

84
00:07:50,710 --> 00:07:54,250
