I'm home!

106
00:09:22,970 --> 00:09:24,930
Ah, welcome back.

107
00:09:24,970 --> 00:09:29,350
Um, Mother, I need to ask
you about something awkward.

108
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:32,480
How did your first date with Father go?

109
