146
00:13:46,810 --> 00:13:49,610
<i>She means the Great Saiyaman thing.</i>

147
00:13:49,650 --> 00:13:51,860
Um, what do you think about it?

148
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:56,120
I think it's very cute.

149
